REPLICATION OF A TUPLE
we can replicate the tuple multiple times by multiplication operator
Eg. animals = ("zebra","horse","cat","dog","lion")
    birds = ("Peacock", "Chicken", "Ostrich", "DODO")

    three = animals * 4
    print(three)
